n."},{"version":"ruby","text":"Whenever LICKITUNG comes across something new, it will unfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things by texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"Whenever LICKITUNG comes across something new, it will unfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things by texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Whenever it sees something unfamiliar, it always licks the object because it memorizes things by texture and taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its tongue is twice the length of its body. It can be moved like an arm for grabbing food and attacking."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon\u2019s. It leaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Instead of hands, it uses its tongue, which is twice its height. Its sticky saliva grips anything."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Instead of hands, it uses its tongue, which is twice its height. Its sticky saliva grips anything."},{"version":"platinum","text":"When it extends its over-six-foot- long tongue, its tail quivers. There is a possibility they are connected."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its tongue has well-developed nerves that run to the very tip, so it can be deftly manipulated."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its long tongue, slathered with a gooey saliva, sticks to anything, so it is very useful."},{"version":"black","text":"When it extends its over-six-foot- long tongue, its tail quivers. There is a possibility they are connected."},{"version":"white","text":"When it extends its over-six-foot- long tongue, its tail quivers. There is a possibility they are connected."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Being licked by its long, saliva-covered tongue leaves a tingling sensation. Extending its tongue retracts its tail."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Being licked by its long, saliva-covered tongue leaves a tingling sensation. Extending its tongue retracts its tail."},{"version":"x","text":"Its long tongue, slathered with a gooey saliva, sticks to anything, so it is very useful."},{"version":"y","text":"Its tongue is twice the length of its body. It can be moved like an arm for grabbing food and attacking."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Whenever Lickitung comes across something new, it will unfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things by texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Whenever Lickitung comes across something new, it will unfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things by texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It checks out whatever\u2019s around it by licking everything. If you don\u2019t clean off a spot where it\u2019s licked you, you\u2019ll break out in a rash!"},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It licks filth clean with its tongue. Whatever it licks always stinks afterward, so whether it\u2019s really clean is...questionable."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its tongue spans almost seven feet and moves more freely than its forelegs. Its licks can cause paralysis."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its tongue spans almost seven feet and moves more freely than its forelegs. Its licks can cause paralysis."},{"version":"sword","text":"If this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s sticky saliva gets on you and you don\u2019t clean it off, an intense itch will set in. The itch won\u2019t go away, either."},{"version":"shield","text":"Bug Pok\u00e9mon are Lickitung\u2019s main food source. This Pok\u00e9mon paralyzes its prey with a lick from its long tongue, then swallows the prey whole."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Wields its long tongue deftly, as though it were an arm. The Pok\u00e9mon's viscous saliva, once it has been collected and boiled down, yields a strong and highly useful adhesive."}],"evo":{"name":"lickitung","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"lickilicky","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":"rollout","known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/108.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/108.png","capture":45,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"hp":2},"forms":[]}